    <descript>
      <abstract>Data available online through the Arkansas Spatial Data Infrastructure at http://gis.arkansas.gov. The Arkansas Department of Health operates as a centralized health department with five public health regions where health services are delivered to the community level.</abstract>
      <purpose>This dataset shows division of state into five zones as designated by the Arkansas Department of Health. The database provides information for use in local and regional cartographic and spatial analysis applications. It is the intention of the Arkansas Geographic Information Systems Board to facilitate dissemination of public data.</purpose>
    </descript>
